COMPONENT NAME: LKM Object Storage to ADWC Copy Direct COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.2.1.4.0 or above
DESCRIPTION This LKM will load data from Oracle Object Storage to Oracle Autonomous Data Warehouse Cloud. It is using dbms_cloud.copy_data() function. This LKM has to be used as standalone, no IKM is needed. It will load data directly into target table. Source attributes must match target column names. Either use data entities with matching attributes or set option GENERATE_FIELD_LIST = false. All target columns will be loaded, not matter whether they are mapped or not. LKM Object Storage to ADWC Copy Direct does not support any transformations.
